== GOAL
Translate lost languages using machine learning.
Decipher lost languages using just a few thousand words.
== DATA
Languages of the world.
== METHODS
Decipherment algorithm, cognate-based decipherment, entity recognition.
== RESULTS
Development of algorithm that deciphered the dead languages.
== ISSUES
What if the translation is wrong.
